<summary>Is this a Sonic Rush fangame?</summary>
<p>Sonic Definitive draws heavy inspiration from the Rush series with its boost-focused 2D gameplay, but it adds its own layer of cinematic sequences, combat mechanics, and a multi-phase boss fight that go beyond what Rush offered.</p>
</details>
